Demonstration of remote driving of a bus at Scania's test site in Sodertalje, Sweden. Part of a research collaboration with Scania, 
using Ericsson's 5G PoC network and Ericssonâ€™s radio network.
The activity was part of a project to explore how future cellular networks can be used in an Intelligent Transport context, 
especially public transportation, and conducted within the Integrated Transportation lab - a collaboration between Ericsson, Scania and KTH.

